data.description: Escape the hustle and bustle of city life and embrace the tranquility of rural living in this picturesque 3-bedroom, 1-bath bungalow, nestled in a beautiful country setting. Here's your opportunity to own a slice of happiness where nature's beauty and simplicity combine. With a large laundry area and welcoming galley style kitchen you have the perfect place to relax and cook the meal of your dreams. Also, there is an extra space with the unfinished basement that has a second outdoor access, your options are open to creating a mother-in-law suite or the extra entertainment room you have always wanted.
